Like the idea of earning a tax free package?Just Available** Mathematics Teacher Required for a Private IB/American School** Tax Free Salary of up to £2500 (15000AED) per month** Free Accommodation and Utilities allowance** Free Flights and Medical Insurance** Start September 2014 (arrive late August for orientation)Our client is a private school offering the IB/US curriculum in the garden city of Al Ain in the UAE.Due to the current post holders contract coming to an end, the Head is currently seeking a Mathematics teacher to join the faculty of this popular private boys' school for the next academic year in September 2014.You will teach across the age/ability range from Years 6 through to 10. Majority of pupils are local Emirati boys' from mid to upper socio backgrounds.You must have a proven track record of academic success, be comfortable teaching in an all boys' environment and be advanced with your ability to incorporate technology with your classroom delivery. You must hold a BA in Mathematics along with a minimum of two years experience to be considered for the role.The Mathematics department is extremely well resourced within the school allowing you to be creative with you lessons.Submit your CV with recent photo to Michael Smith on the details below or click "Apply Now" for immediate consideration on this role.For all international posts go to www.academicsltd.co.uk and www.acdemicsltd.com.au
